    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Backend-neutral MIDI preview renderer facade.</para>
<para><ref refid="namespaceRADMedia" kindref="compound">RADMedia</ref> includes a lightweight built-in MIDI preview renderer so applications can play edited clips without depending on FluidSynth. Loading a SoundFont validates/selects the preset source for track configuration; richer SF2/SF3 sample playback can be attached later behind this same facade. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
